<p>Cool Stuff Found and Quick Tips in the same episode? You bet! John F. Braun and Dave Hamilton aim to deliver for you each and every week. And since the goal is to learn &lt;em&gt;at least&lt;/em&gt; four new things each week, some options might include keeping your Mac awaken &lt;em&gt;only&lt;/em&gt; when you like, managing Siri&#039;s holidays when set for a foreign voice, yet another replacement for DeskConnect, and a segment one listener calls &quot;follow the dots.&quot; You&#039;ll just have to listen to see what &lt;em&gt;that&lt;/em&gt; is all about. Press play and enjoy, folks!Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
